@startuml Industrial_Wearable_AI_Context
!include theme.puml
title Industrial Wearable AI — System Context (C4 Style)

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F0FDFA
  BorderColor #0d9488
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #EFF6FF
  BorderColor #1e40af
}

actor "Worker" as Worker #EFF6FF
actor "Supervisor" as Supervisor #EFF6FF

rectangle "Industrial Wearable AI System" as System #F0FDFA {

  rectangle "Wearable" as Wearable #EFF6FF {
    [ESP32 + IMU\nBLE] as Dev
  }

  rectangle "Edge Gateway" as Edge #F0FDFA {
    [Python\nBLE → Buffer → ML → API] as EdgeProc
  }

  rectangle "Backend" as Backend #F0FDFA {
    [FastAPI\nREST + WebSocket] as API
    [PostgreSQL] as DB
  }

  rectangle "Dashboard" as Dashboard #F0FDFA {
    [React\nLive Overview\nAlerts\nSessions] as Web
  }
}

Worker --> Wearable : wears
Wearable --> Edge : BLE\n(IMU stream)
Edge --> Backend : HTTP\n(events, sensor)
Backend --> Dashboard : WebSocket\n(live state)
Supervisor --> Dashboard : HTTP\n(view, login)

note right of System
  **Purpose:** Real-time visibility
  into worker activity and risk
  (ergonomic, fatigue) for
  textile manufacturing SMEs.
end note

@enduml
